{
    "attributes": {
        "action": "Recognise nonbinary gender identities in law and in official identity documents",
        "additional_details": "In the recent past the UK government repeatedly acknowledged the existence of nonbinary people, and it should provide documents accordingly.",
        "background": "Make nonbinary gender markers possible on any official document where a gender marker is required, e.g. passport, gender recognition certificate, marriage documents, death certificate.",
